    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that amazing fresh feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and looked after, this is the one for you. Drop me a message, I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
      "price": 46500.0,
