    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains in peak mechanical form, exhibiting flawless compression across all cylinders with a silent Double-VANOS system. The chassis integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension retains its factory-spec damping with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. Power is sent through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring tactile feedback and optimal traction. Every fluid line is bone-dry, and the underbody shows no signs of oxidation or heat cycling fatigue. The exterior finish and Nappa leather interior are preserved in a state that reflects minimal mileage and climate-controlled storage. This is a definitive example of atmospheric engineering, free of the common mechanical foibles associated with the chassis.",
      "price": 46500.0,
