      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features the original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014absolutely no swirls, chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin retains that fresh leather scent; the bolsters are firm, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a full binder of records included. It starts instantly, idles silently, and shifts with precision. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated example for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
